flowchart TD
    Offchain[Off-chain Route Builder] -->|route plan + accounts + min_out| Axis[Axis Program]
    Axis -->|Validate asset policy| Policy[Asset Execution Policy]
    Axis -->|Validate route| Route[Approved Route Registry]
    Axis -->|Validate pricing source| Pricing[Pricing Source Registry]
    Axis -->|Dispatch to adapter| Adapter[Venue Adapter]

    Adapter --> Orca[Orca Whirlpool]
    Adapter --> RaydiumCPMM[Raydium CPMM]
    Adapter --> PumpSwap[PumpSwap]
    Adapter --> RaydiumCLMM[Raydium CLMM]
    Adapter --> Meteora[Meteora DLMM]

    Orca --> Delta[Actual Balance Delta]
    RaydiumCPMM --> Delta
    PumpSwap --> Delta
    RaydiumCLMM --> Delta
    Meteora --> Delta

    Delta -->|Verify actual_received >= min_out| Axis
    Axis --> Accounting[Mint / Redeem Accounting]
